MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2012-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 28th October, 2012
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 28th October, 2012:
Shri M. Veerappa Moily relinquished the charge of (a) the office of the Minister of
Corporate Affairs; and (b) the additional charge of the office of the Minister of Power
and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Petroleum and Natural Gas;
Shri S. Jaipal Reddy relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Petroleum
and Natural Gas and assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Science and
Technology and the charge of the office of the Minister of Earth Sciences;
1.
2.

office of the Minister of Parliamentary Affairs;
3.

charge of (a) the office of the Minister of Science and Technology; (b) the office of the
Minister of Earth Sciences; and (c) the office of the Minister of Micro, Small and Medium
Enterprises;
4.

Development. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of
